    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.3999999602
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "本日の主役成宮すず様のお帰りですわよ～！\n誕生日にもお仕事をするなんて……私、勤勉ですわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "本日の主役成宮すず様のお帰りですわよ～！\n誕生日にもお仕事をするなんて……私、勤勉ですわ～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.9666666269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.7333332936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　こんな所にポテトチップスが落ちてますわ！\nしかも、点々とどこかに続いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あら？　こんな所にポテトチップスが落ちてますわ！\nしかも、点々とどこかに続いて……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9333332936,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5533.3333333,
          "startTime": 25.4666666269
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_garden-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 25.1166676442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "庭で途切れましたわ……これは一体……！？\nひー！　木の枝にポテトチップスの袋が生えてますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "庭で途切れましたわ……これは一体……！？\nひー！　木の枝にポテトチップスの袋が生えてますわ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1333348195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まさか、ついにポテトチップスの木が\n爆誕しましたの！？　これは大スクープですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ま、まさか、ついにポテトチップスの木が\n爆誕しましたの！？　これは大スクープですわ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2999999602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、でも、さすがにそんな訳は……\nもしかして誰かのイタズラですの……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いや、でも、さすがにそんな訳は……\nもしかして誰かのイタズラですの……！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0333332936,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4266.668192499999,
          "startTime": 58.3000014861
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "やぁ、すず。やけに慌ててどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "やぁ、すず。やけに慌ててどうしたの？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2000025034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "葵！　今、この木にポテトチップスが生えているのを\n発見したんですの。イタズラとは思うのですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "葵！　今、この木にポテトチップスが生えているのを\n発見したんですの。イタズラとは思うのですけど……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2361829679,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5063.8169922999905,
          "startTime": 71.2999999602
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "どれどれ……なるほど本当に生えてきているね\n世紀の大発見だよ、すず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "どれどれ……なるほど本当に生えてきているね\n世紀の大発見だよ、すず",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0333332936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあこれは本当にポテトチップスのなる木ですの！？\n今朝見た夢が正夢になるなんて……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "じゃあこれは本当にポテトチップスのなる木ですの！？\n今朝見た夢が正夢になるなんて……！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7333332936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇすず、ちょっと木を揺らしてみようよ。もっと\n落ちてくるんじゃないかな。ほら、一緒に……せーの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ねぇすず、ちょっと木を揺らしてみようよ。もっと\n落ちてくるんじゃないかな。ほら、一緒に……せーの",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0666666269,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8133.329264199986,
          "startTime": 96.8000025033
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "凄いですわ！　大量に降ってきますわ～！\nもう未来永劫、ポテトチップスに困りませんわー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "凄いですわ！　大量に降ってきますわ～！\nもう未来永劫、ポテトチップスに困りませんわー！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4333332936,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_plasticbag-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 98.166673239
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_plasticbag-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2209.993387899999,
          "startTime": 100.3766666269
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "まだ上の方に生えてるよ。あ、てっぺんに岡山限定\nオムライス味も見えるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "まだ上の方に生えてるよ。あ、てっぺんに岡山限定\nオムライス味も見えるね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4999999602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "限定味まで生えるなんて！　とても親切な木ですわ！\n……ん？　袋の陰に隠れて紐のような物が……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "限定味まで生えるなんて！　とても親切な木ですわ！\n……ん？　袋の陰に隠れて紐のような物が……？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5999999602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "あらら、バレちゃったか。僕からのサプライズだよ\nすず、誕生日おめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あらら、バレちゃったか。僕からのサプライズだよ\nすず、誕生日おめでとう",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6333332936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり！　最初からおかしいと思ってましたのよ！\nもっと普通にお祝いしてくださいまし～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "やっぱり！　最初からおかしいと思ってましたのよ！\nもっと普通にお祝いしてくださいまし～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.6666666269,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9100.000039799994,
          "startTime": 149.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "だって、普通じゃつまらないでしょ？\nでも食べ過ぎには注意してね、それじゃあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "だって、普通じゃつまらないでしょ？\nでも食べ過ぎには注意してね、それじゃあ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7666625579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　葵ったら……はぁ……夢で見た\nポテトチップスの木の実現は程遠いですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "もう！　葵ったら……はぁ……夢で見た\nポテトチップスの木の実現は程遠いですわね……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0666320403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_53_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "でも……どうして葵は私の夢の内容を知って\nいたんでしょう……？　まったく不思議な人ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "でも……どうして葵は私の夢の内容を知って\nいたんでしょう……？　まったく不思議な人ですわ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.6999653737,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}